---

**Why each version is pinned this way:**

| Package | Version | Reason |
|---|---|---|
| `@solana/spl-token` | `^0.4.9` | 0.4.x exports `NATIVE_MINT`, `createSyncNativeInstruction`, `createSetAuthorityInstruction`, `AuthorityType` — all required by the new code |
| `@solana/web3.js` | `^1.98.0` | Must stay on v1.x — v2 is a complete rewrite with a different API that would break every import |
| `bs58` | `^5.0.0` | v5 has a default export (`import bs58 from 'bs58'` then `bs58.decode()`) — v6 switched to named-only exports which would crash on startup |
| `dotenv` | `^16.4.5` | v16 supports `import 'dotenv/config'` syntax used at the top of index.js |
| `express` | `^4.21.1` | Stable v4, v5 is still RC |
| `node-cache` | `^5.1.2` | Current stable, no breaking changes expected |
| `node-telegram-bot-api` | `^0.64.0` | Latest stable with working polling mode |

